          <h4>Inland Empire family housing</h4>
          <p>Ontario · <a href="/rancho-cucamonga/">Rancho Cucamonga</a> · Riverside · Fontana · Moreno Valley · Murrieta</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>Related LG and cross-brand pages</h2>
      <ul class="related-links">
        <li><a href="/brands/signature-kitchen-suite-refrigerator-repair/">SKS refrigerator repair (LG-launched luxury) →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/brands/samsung-refrigerator-repair/">Samsung refrigerator repair (Korean competitor) →</a></li>
